Scenario name : Success login with valid data user

No.    Test Step                                       Expected results
1.      Open WeMine or WeMineOffice                      Show login page
2.      Input username with existing data                Field username accepting inputs
3.      Hit button next or continue                      Apps will send request to /user/who
4.      If success apps shows Microsoft login            Microsoft login page shows field password  
5.      Input with valid password                        Microsoft success validate credentials
6.      Apps send request to /user/me                    Success get profile user
7.      Apps send request for list of user               Success get list of user
8.      Apps will fetch data for each endpoint           Progress bar updates for each endpoint is successfully processed
9.      All master data has been downloaded              The progress bar reaches 100% and changes to 'Complete'
10.     The app displays a prompt                        “Restart required to apply new master data”
11.     Restart apps                                      After restarting, the user is directed to the Dashboard/Home Screen, and all master data is synchronized & ready to use            


Scenario name : Failed login with invalid data username

No.    Test Step                                       Expected results
1.      Open WeMine or WeMineOffice                      Show login page
2.      Input username with invalid username             Field username will declined cause invalid data  


Scenario name : Failed login with invalid data password

No.    Test Step                                       Expected results
1.      Open WeMine or WeMineOffice                      Show login page
2.      Input username with existing data                Field username accepting inputs
3.      Hit button next or continue                      Apps will send request to /user/who
4.      If success apps shows Microsoft login            Microsoft login page shows field password 
5.      Input with invalid password                      Declined login because wrong password
